text: Nocardioides daecheongensis is a gram-positive, aerobic, non-spore-forming and non-motile bacterium from the genus Nocardioides that has been isolated from forest soil from Incheon on Daecheong Island, South Korea.Deutsche Sampling von Mikroorganismen und Zellkulturen == References == ==External links== *Type strain of Nocardioides daecheongensis at BacDive - the Bacterial Diversity Metadatabase daecheongensis Category:Bacteria described in 2014
title: Nocardioides daecheongensis
